  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently the validator client logs `Awaiting activation` when doppelganger protection is enabled, which is a bit confusing because it's the same message for validators that aren't active at all. I think we should override this message when doppelganger protection is enabled to say something more informative like `Validators paused while waiting for doppelganger detection, reactivation_epoch: <epoch>`\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse v3.1.0\r\n",
